  "detailed_description": "\"Girls on Campus, from Freshmen to Faculty, All Fall for Me!\" is an immersive video game of love simulation. What's different is that the characteristics of the current cool drama are integrated into the game. The real-life kneeling and licking spare tires do not exist. Just give me brainless girls chasing boys! Various super sweet close-ups, have a hearty love (or several) with beautiful girls!<br><br>Lin Yan, a senior, is carefree, simple-minded and strong-willed.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/42eaa717e6c4842bfa729d3c75e12459.poster.avif?t=1723778314\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/42eaa717e6c4842bfa729d3c75e12459.webm?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/42eaa717e6c4842bfa729d3c75e12459.mp4?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lin Ran, a junior, Lin Yan's sister, has a cute and lovely image in front of people. She has a bad relationship with her strong sister since she was a child, so she gradually learned to hide her true feelings.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/d02144253dfa0064b0c836f8b83e593f.poster.avif?t=1723778314\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/d02144253dfa0064b0c836f8b83e593f.webm?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/d02144253dfa0064b0c836f8b83e593f.mp4?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Shen Meng, cold on the outside, weak on the inside, easily manipulated by the strong opposite sex.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/ea8ded964fa71dc7d7c4b16ac4e65585.poster.avif?t=1723778314\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/ea8ded964fa71dc7d7c4b16ac4e65585.webm?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/ea8ded964fa71dc7d7c4b16ac4e65585.mp4?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chen Xi, not long after the biological mother of Lin Yan and Lin Ran died, was married to their father and became their stepmother.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/a9992a24fd4b20c5d9d621cf67a3e398.poster.avif?t=1723778314\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/a9992a24fd4b20c5d9d621cf67a3e398.webm?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/a9992a24fd4b20c5d9d621cf67a3e398.mp4?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Su Qing, a mysterious junior, a girl who wants to avenge her sister.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/24362f6a078d154cd530141104863c33.poster.avif?t=1723778314\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/24362f6a078d154cd530141104863c33.webm?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029990/extras/24362f6a078d154cd530141104863c33.mp4?t=1723778314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Product Features</strong><br><br>First-person perspective experience——<br>The first-person perspective setting provides a strong sense of immersion, giving players an immersive and sweet love experience.<br><br>Multiple lines with open endings——<br>Each heroine has her own story line, and a fully developed ending is waiting for you to explore<br><br>Beautiful figure, hearty——<br>Five beautiful heroines, doing their best to perform their roles to bring you one or more love fantasies!",
